<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<game romname="wwfmania" gamename="WWF: Wrestlemania (rev 1.30 08/10/95)" numPlayers="2" alternating="0" mirrored="1" usesService="0" tilt="1" cocktail="0">
	<miscDetails>
This game has the same mame-related layout problems as the mk games.  The X pattern applies.  Press punch and kick at the same time to run.      Note that the punch buttons are on the top row and the kick buttons are on the bottom, unlike the mk games and similar to sf games.
	</miscDetails>
	<player number="1" numButtons="5">
		<controls>
